body_html: @danbri - Not much yet: I've been low on time myself as well. My current goal is to get Bazel 2 running on a RPi, then put out new binaries for the 0.8 release once the candidate has gone gold. Afterward, hopefully I'll have some time to dig deeper into which operations are causing headaches on the Pi.
